fr.enseeiht.danck.voice_analyzer

Class VoiceAnalyzerMulti

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.enseeiht.danck.voice_analyzer.VoiceAnalyzer
      • fr.enseeiht.danck.voice_analyzer.VoiceAnalyzerMulti

  • public class VoiceAnalyzerMulti
extends VoiceAnalyzer
    A 'MutliThread' version of the VoiceAnalyzer. Use GroomerThread in a separated Thread instead of a simple Groomer. Allows to be manipulated by only one Thread.
    Author:
    Anaël Megna, Kilian Boulhaïs, Cyrius Nugier
